# Recheck Project Cursor Rules

## Virtual Environment
Always use the virtualenv at `~/.virtualenvs/recheck` for this project.

When running Python commands:
```bash
source ~/.virtualenvs/recheck/bin/activate
```

## Testing
Run tests with:
```bash
source ~/.virtualenvs/recheck/bin/activate && make tests
```

Or for quick tests without coverage:
```bash
source ~/.virtualenvs/recheck/bin/activate && pytest tests/ -x --tb=short
```

## Project Structure
- `recheck/` - Main package
- `tests/` - Test suite (pytest)
- Use `make tests` to run full test suite with coverage

## Code Style
- Python 3.9+ with type hints
- Dataclasses for data structures
- Follow existing patterns in the codebase
